name: baby blue sweater -
description:
Hand-knitted sweater made with a 100% wool yarn. The color of the yarn is baby blue with a gray tinge. This beautiful and delicate pullover comes with short sleeves. The sleeves are a modified version of the raglan sleeve, these ones are better suited to the natural curve of the shoulder. The front and back of the garment have an irregular pattern and the front is asymmetric with respect to the rear. 
All seams have been made by hand.
